---
title: Brown-Butter Scallops over Summer Greens with Feta and Tarragon Dressing
description: This delightful salad boasts golden-seared scallops in brown butter. Bursting with veggies and complemented by charred sweetness from the corn and crusty garlic ciabatta, this summery plate of deliciousness is practically restaurant quality!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/brown-butter-scallops-over-summer-greens-79af934d.jpg
